---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Paving & Stonemasonry Cardinia Shire | Full Service Area | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Paving, stonemasonry, retaining-wall and hardscape contractors across Cardinia Shire - Officer, Cardinia Lakes, Beaconsfield, Pakenham, Heritage Springs. AS 3727 + AS 4678 engineered. Class M reactive-clay base spec."
  canonical="https://officerpavingco.com.au/cardinia-shire/">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cardinia Shire &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>Paving &amp; stonemasonry across <span class="accent">Cardinia Shire</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From the Officer growth corridor in the west through Cardinia Lakes,
        Beaconsfield, Pakenham and Heritage Springs to the rural-residential
        acreage of the Pakenham Upper and Beaconsfield Upper foothills. Driveways,
        patios, pool surrounds and engineered AS 4678 retaining walls on
        Class M reactive clay.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free site visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>Full local guides - typical block size, soil class, council crossover process, what we usually spec.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/pakenham/">Pakenham</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other Cardinia Shire suburbs we work in.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Beaconsfield Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Berwick Waters</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Officer South</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Arena Estate</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Timbertop</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lakeside (Pakenham)</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Nar Nar Goon</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Tynong</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bunyip</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Garfield</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Maryknoll</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Iona</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cora Lynn</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Two markets, one trade.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Growth-corridor zone</strong> (Officer, Cardinia Lakes, Berwick
          Waters, Arena, Timbertop, Heritage Springs, Lakeside Pakenham):
          young-family new builds on 350-600m&sup2; lots. Default brief is
          exposed-aggregate driveway, bluestone or sandstone alfresco patio,
          occasional sub-1m segmental-block retaining wall. Class M reactive-clay
          engineering on every job - 100mm slab, SL82 mesh, 100mm compacted
          Class 3 base, polymeric-sanded paver joints, edge restraints.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Established / acreage zone</strong> (Beaconsfield, Beaconsfield
          Upper, Pakenham township, Pakenham Upper): older brick veneer or
          weatherboard homes on 600m&sup2;-5+ha lots. Often replacement work
          - lifting failed 25-40 year old concrete and re-pouring to current
          AS 3727 spec. Sloping blocks here mean engineered AS 4678 retaining
          walls on most jobs. Large-format bluestone or granite paver driveways
          ($180-$260/m&sup2;) suit the heritage aesthetic better than
          modern segmental block.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Permit &amp; engineering thresholds.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>No permit:</strong> Back-yard paving with no kerb crossover and no retaining over 1m (most patios, paths, pool surrounds).</li>
          <li><strong>Cardinia Shire crossover permit:</strong> Any work that crosses the kerb, footpath or nature strip. Fee ~$200-$350, slab to council&rsquo;s IPWEA-aligned spec (125mm, SL82 mesh, set widths). Council inspects at pour and completion.</li>
          <li><strong>Retaining-wall building permit:</strong> Any wall over 1m retained height needs an AS 4678 engineer-designed wall + Cardinia Shire building permit. From 0.6m on Class H reactive clay we recommend engineering anyway.</li>
          <li><strong>Heritage Overlay:</strong> A few specific Pakenham township and older Beaconsfield streets. Planning approval needed before changing front-of-house presentation including driveway material choice.</li>
          <li><strong>Stormwater detention:</strong> Cardinia Shire may require on-lot detention for major paving works on existing properties - we check at quote stage.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five services</span>
      <h2>What we lay.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/driveway-paving/"><h3>Driveway paving</h3><p>$90-$260/m&sup2;. Exposed aggregate, stencilled, segmental block, bluestone. Cardinia Shire crossover permit included.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/patio-paving/"><h3>Patio paving</h3><p>$140-$260/m&sup2;. Bluestone, sandstone, travertine, porcelain. Polymeric-sanded joints, edge restraints.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/pool-surrounds/"><h3>Pool surrounds</h3><p>$180-$280/m&sup2;. R11/P5 non-slip natural stone and porcelain. Bullnose copers, chemical-safe edging.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/retaining-walls/"><h3>Retaining walls</h3><p>$300-$600/m&sup2; face area. AS 4678 engineered. Sock-wrapped ag-drain + 20mm drainage rock backfill standard.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/segmental-paving/"><h3>Segmental paving</h3><p>$60-$140/m&sup2;. Repair, re-lay or extend existing block, brick or segmental paving. Cheaper than replacement.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free site visit anywhere in Cardinia Shire.</h2>
        <p>Growth-corridor new build or acreage replacement. Soil-class check, slope and drainage review, material samples on-site. Fixed quote within 7 days.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
